dct_title_s: A new map of the most considerable plantations of the English in America
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. "Dedicated to His Highness William Duke of Glocester." Insets: New Scotland.--I. of Jamaica.--I. of Barbados.--Bermudaz or Sommers Isles.--Carolina. From: A new sett of maps ... / by Edward Wells. [London : s.n., ca. 1743] Date of publication from Burden. Historic Maps copy imperfect: upper right corner torn.
